            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="font-size:18px; width:20px; vertical-align: top; padding-right:8px;">→</td>
              <td style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">The agreement supports Ukraine’s goal of becoming an EU member. It doesn’t explicitly state that Ukraine’s EU accession will come across as a conflict of interest</td>
