         <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
        She also urged Trump to halt weapons smuggling across the border from the US. These smuggled arms have made Mexico one of the world's most violent countries. Trump has often complained about cross-border drug smuggling and undocumented immigrants. 
         </p>
         <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
          Meanwhile, the US military has set up a <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-5-may-25-spotlight-h1-2-second-military-zone" target="_blank">second military zone</a>, “Texas National Defense Area,” a 63-mile strip running east from the Texas-New Mexico border in El Paso to curb illegal migration. According to the Pentagon, the detainees will be handed over to US Customs and Border Protection (CBP) or other civilian law enforcement. 
         </p>
        
